rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0020
rows.name: What the hell is going on here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0030
rows.name: Let's continue the investigation and hope the analysis team produces results, shall we?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0040
rows.name:
You saying that since we're still moving right now,
we shouldn't panic?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0060
rows.name: But, remaining in such an uncertain state like this[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0080
rows.name:
You are the Commander.
What good does it do to stir up the squad's anxiety?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0140
rows.name: But right now, our comrades in the Central Life are also...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0150
rows.name: Desperately continuing the investigation while fighting that same anxiety.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0160
rows.name: Sacrificing their own time to do it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0170
rows.name: So, let's trust them and wait.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0200
rows.name:
Everyone is working hard,
yet I was only thinking of myself[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs30010100_MSG0230
rows.name: You aren't even a [System:Ruby rt=B.B. ]Blue Blood[/System:Ruby] to begin with[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]
